Intelligent Literature Exploration

Serendipity is too important to be left to chance.

HELPING MODERN RESEARCHERS

Connect the Dots

Humans are the best filters of information. We see this in researchers who create their own pristine dataset of papers using citation managers.

There’s just too much information to keep in the context of our brains to take advantage of this information.

That's why we've developed cutting-edge metascience intelligent search and retrieval tools to give researchers a peripheral vision to their papers while thinking.

INTELLIGENT SEARCH & RETRIEVAL

Organize Human Knowledge

Our tools go beyond keyword-based searches and traditional indexing methods. They use hybrid-search, analyzing the semantic context, relationships, and underlying concepts within scientific literature, giving you unparalleled access to the information you need.

OUR MISSION

Accelerate science via intelligence augmentation

We want to enable researchers to have thoughts and connections they would not been able to have otherwise. Outsiders assume that scientific discoveries are obvious in retrospect because of the inherent assumption of perfect information (ex. ‘Since paper X and paper Y were out, Z should have been obvious’). We want to enable researchers to actually have more obvious connections.
